# Jack-O'Lantern (JACK)

Jack-O'Lantern by Porkjet. Jack-O'Lantern themed probe cores in seven sizes. All the modcons.

#### Adopted for curation by [@`zer0Kerbal`][LINK:zer0Kerbal], originally by [@`PorkJet`][LINK:porkjet]

![Mod Version][MOD:shld:latest] ![KSP version][KSP:shld]  [![License CC BY-NC 4.0][LICENSE:shld]][LICENSE:url]  

[![Curseforge][CURSFG:shld]][CURSFG:url] [![CKAN][CKAN:shd]][CKAN:url] [![GitHub][GITHUB:shld]][GITHUB:url] [![SpaceDock][SPCDCK:shld]][SPCDCK:url]  

![Code][CODE:shld] ![KSP-AVC][AVC:shld] ![Validate AVC .version files][AVCVLD:shld]  

###### _brought to you by KGEx_

***

## Features 

This parts pack adds seven different sized Jack-O’Lantern themed probe cores

- Five different sizes with all the modcons
- TweakScale configs are included.

***

![Trick-r-Treat!][IMG:hero:0]  
![Family Jack-O'-Lantern][IMG:hero:1]  


#### Cabin notes  

> - The mod contains five sizes of Jack-O'Lantern themed probe cores with all the modcons.
> - Future Plans: lol. Except compatibility patches, keep it working with future KSP updates.
> - Have a request? Glad to have them, kindly submit through GitHub.
> - Would love to see one or more textures that could be set as variants. Would need help with the textures. :D
